Making Ramen

1 Prepare the Ramen
 1.1 get ramen
  If there's ramen in the pantry?
    1.1.1 get the ramen from the pantry
    1.1.2 bring ramen to sink
  If there's not
    1.1.1 get the ramen from the cabinet
    1.1.2 bring ramen to sink
 1.2 fill the ramen cup
  1.2.1 open the ramen cup
  1.2.2 take out the flavor pack
  1.2.3 turn on the sink
  1.2.4 fill to the line
  1.2.5 turn off the sink
2 Cook the ramen
  2.1 bring the ramen to the microwave
    2.1.1 open up the microwave
    2.1.2 place ramen inside
    2.1.3 close the microwave
    2.1.4 set time for 3 minutes
    2.1.5 wait 3 minutes
    2.1.6 open the microwave
    2.1.7 take out Ramen
    2.1.8 close the microwave
  2.2 Let cool
